Published Online: 31 August 1998
Accepted: September 1987
A unitary multiconfigurational coupled‐cluster method: Theory and applications
J. Chem. Phys. 88 , 993 (1988); https://doi.org/10.1063/1.454125
Mark R. Hoffmann and Jack Simons
more... View Affiliations

    Department of Chemistry, University of Utah, Salt Lake City, Utah 84112

    PDF
    CHORUS

